StdFM fgfEIw pf-344_ pf-text-1">Health and character declaration</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-346_ pf-text-1">Professional indemnity arrangement</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-348_ pf-text-1">Confirmation.</li></ul><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/pages/online-cpd-courses-training-cpd-accredited-elearning-courses" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-ezrfit cEhRZf pf-350_ pf-button-1"><em><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 175, 82);"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Click here</span></span></strong></em> to explore our wide range of accredited eLearning courses, each providing CPD hours to help you meet your revalidation requirements.</a></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-352_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/NMC_Revalidation_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1716896622" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/NMC_Revalidation_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1716896622 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/NMC_Revalidation_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1716896622 320w" width="1333" height="1333" alt="NMC Revalidation -  ComplyPlus LMS - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="NMC Revalidation -  ComplyPlus LMS - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-cTTcKX gslXuF pf-353_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-feac" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-354_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-355_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc